<br>
But some points.<br>
<br>
MC3 should give an epic sorceror closer to 10%, not sure how you got your numbers.<br>
<br>
Base medding mana regen is 20 at 57 and 58 I know for sure since I have tested it thouroughly when I was determining that MC was broken.<br>
<br>
The fudge factor on Twiddle's formula is off somehow. I would suspect that base regen for a sorceror would be 21, possibly maybe 22. That would put MC3 about 11%. With no FT or or buffs other than epic skin and 60 flappy.<br>
<br>
Of course for raiding MC has frequently ZERO effect.<br>
<br>
Also the assumption that crits do not produce more aggro, while an assumption I share, is still an assumption.<br>
