<br>
My suggestion is to march AA as fast as possible at levels 55 - 58, when XP flows much faster during quad kites, and flip the XP bar to &quot;level&quot; at 59 and 60, when there is a much smaller selection of targets to quad.<br>
<br>
Level is everything.  But I suspect (haven't tested it) that XP/hour comes much faster at lev 55 than it does at lev 60.<br>
<br>
